<plot>Jake and Jimmy Pelagrino are two of America's most wanted...at least that's what they tell themselves. Allegedly the masterminds behind one of the largest heists in American history, the Pelagrino brothers have agreed to an exclusive one-time interview. Tune in as the mysterious Pelagrinos explain events that led to the daring heist of The Lost Idol of Halicarnassus. Along the way, the brothers detail their encounter with a man known only as Dangerous Dino and his inside informant, Jade McGee. 'Infamous' is an award-winning Mockumentary that shows you don't have to be a genius to pull off the crime of the century...all you need is a little imagination.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?264718</url></doc>
